<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="background-color: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span></span><br>I’m still struggling to reach you since you were referred to us by On the Tools.<br><br>It’s likely you are looking at lots of different providers for your business insurance policy. So, here are the reasons why the team at Kingsbridge stand out from our competitors:</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"></p><ul><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Real people, real support:&nbsp;</b>quick access to dedicated UK-based insurance specialists.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>UK-based claims centre:&nbsp;</b>rapid, responsive claims processing managed by an in-house claims team.&nbsp;</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>There when you need them:</b>&nbsp;strong history of fair, fast, and hassle-free claims processing.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Tailored industry expertise:</b>&nbsp;cover specifically built for contractors, freelancers, and small business owners.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>No hidden fees:&nbsp;</b>transparent pricing with no unexpected costs.</font></li></ul><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Let’s catch up on the phone so I can make sure I provide you with the best policy for you at the best price.&nbsp;<b><a href="https://calendly.com/d/crv2-4cb-zcj/kingsbridge-insurance-call-back-on-the-tools">Book a call with me</a></b>.<br><br></font><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Not able to answer calls during the day?</span></b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Send me a message on WhatsApp using&nbsp;<b><a href="https://go.kingsbridge.co.uk/ott-ar-whatsapp">07917 515428</a></b>&nbsp;and I’ll contact you via message instead.<br></span><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br>Alternatively, contact me on&nbsp;<b>01242 808 740</b>. Our office is open 8:00am-5:30pm, Monday-Friday.&nbsp;<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>I look forward to hearing from you soon!<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
